---
// mockups/TimelineMockup.astro
// Step 4 visual — success-path event log ending in a customer reply.
---
<div class="timeline">
  <div class="tl-rail"></div>

  <div class="tl-event">
    <div class="tl-dot done"></div>
    <div class="tl-head">
      <span class="tl-title">PR #1284 merged into <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--ink)">main</span></span>
      <span class="tl-time">May 19 · 14:22</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-meta">by ube[bot] · reviewed by @maya.t</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tl-event">
    <div class="tl-dot done"></div>
    <div class="tl-head">
      <span class="tl-title">Released in v2.4.3</span>
      <span class="pill pill-muted">beta · 10%</span>
      <span class="tl-time">May 20 · 09:10</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tl-event">
    <div class="tl-dot done"></div>
    <div class="tl-head">
      <span class="tl-title">v2.4.3 rolling out</span>
      <span class="pill pill-success">prod · 100%</span>
      <span class="tl-time">May 22</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tl-event">
    <div class="tl-dot"></div>
    <div class="tl-head">
      <span class="tl-title">Reply sent to original reporter</span>
      <span class="tl-time">May 22 · 11:04</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-meta">App Store review · @sarahk_dev (★ → pending update)</div>
    <div class="tl-msg">
      Thanks for the report — the crash on the video review tap is fixed in v2.4.3, which started rolling out today. If you give the new version a spin, we'd love to hear if it's holding up on your end.
      <div class="tl-by"><span class="avatar">U</span>sent by Ube</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
